data.description: Welcome to the inviting ambiance of 1848 Emerald Drive, where every corner exudes comfort and charm. This delightful residence welcomes you with three spacious bedrooms, perfect for relaxation and rejuvenation. Accompanied by two full bathrooms, including modern fixtures and ample storage, convenience meets style seamlessly. Entertain guests in the separate dining and living area, or explore the two level upstairs bonus room, offering endless possibilities for customization to suit your lifestyle.  And be sure to check out the HUGE walk-in closet/storage room on the second floor.  The sunroom beckons with its warmth and natural light, providing a serene space to unwind and enjoy panoramic views of the surrounding low maintenance landscape. Step into the kitchen, equipped with appliances, and discover culinary inspiration at every turn. Nestled in a desirable neighborhood, this residence offers not just comfort, but also convenience, with easy access to local amenities and attractions. Don't miss the opportunity to make 1848 Emerald Drive your new sanctuary and experience the perfect blend of comfort, versatility, and charm!
